com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services.admin

Class ShowtimesAdmin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.danielly.jsf.cinema.services.admin.ShowtimesAdmin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Named(value="showtime_data")
 @RequestScoped
public class ShowtimesAdmin
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    The Class ShowtimesAdmin provides methods to manage the showtimes in the GUI interface. It handle the inputs, query the database and notify the user when needed.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Gil Danielly
